text: Corinne Le Moal (born 10 November 1954) is a French rower. She competed in the women's single sculls event at the 1992 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1954 births Category:Living people Category:French female rowers Category:Olympic rowers of France Category:Rowers at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Eure
